📈 Key Insights Generated
Identified the highest revenue-generating books and genres.
Discovered customer purchasing trends and repeat buyers.
Evaluated author-wise sales performance.
Analyzed inventory levels to identify low-stock books.
Measured total revenue generated from book sales.
Determined the most frequently purchased books.
Identified high-value customers and their locations.
Calculated remaining stock after order fulfillment.

